<h2>🏛 History</h2>

<p>
The islands were originally settled by Micronesian peoples thousands of years ago. They later came under Spanish, German, Japanese, and United States administration.
</p>

<p>
The :contentReference[oaicite:15]{index=15} became self-governing in 1979 and gained full independence in free association with the United States in 1986.
</p>

